    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>PictoRobot</i></strong> is a platform game in which you control a robot capable of shooting paint bubbles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level represents a hidden image: its colors have been replaced by numbered squares on the walls. You will have to explore the levels to reach all the numbered walls and color them with the right paint bubbles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The levels have different sizes: there are simple ones and others more difficult. They contain several elements such as teleporters, moving platforms, fans… The challenges in the levels are varied: sometimes you have to show skill by avoiding lasers, be quick to reach a summit before the platforms disappear or solve a puzzle by activating the right switches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many levels are available:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t50 levels are included.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tFree seasonal updates contain new levels.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tA level editor allows you to create your own levels.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tThanks to the free <i>Steam Workshop</i> feature, you can publish your creations and download levels created by other players.</p></li></ul>",
